casebody.data:
Jennifer Anne WOLSKI
v.
NORTH CAROLINA DIVISION OF MOTOR VEHICLES and the Commissioner of Motor Vehicles No. 137P17 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 17, 2017 Allen C. Brotherton, Attorney at Law, Charlotte, for Wolski, Jennifer Anne. Kathryn E. Hathcock, Assistant Attorney General, for NC Division of Motor Vehicles, et al.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 25th of April 2017 by Respondents in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th of August 2017."
